{"tid":1754684,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Hard Disk 死左可以去邊到整","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T14:28:01.000Z","uid":206272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad20b20cc704452bceb7333df39e1c8f87d123e","tid":1754684,"uid":206272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"個Hard Disk 用左7年,<br />\n最近不停 load 唔到入window<br />\nReboot 左多次之後，依加直情讀唔到data<br />\n有電到亦都有轉。<br />\n<br />\n入面放左好多相, SSP 有無邊間鋪可以攞返data<br />\n同大約要整幾錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0368dcf0fe3426e7b9a1124eb1c79a17a6ed727","tid":1754684,"uid":70227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429a8d0b5d4105db533a94241cc7e2da15080c5a","tid":1754684,"uid":309753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:54:16.000Z","msg":"可能係HDD 個電流不穩定,<br />\n要拎去俾人check同幫你recover 番入面啲資料, 再過落個新HDD 度.<br />\n我之前壞左個500gb HDD, 又係差唔多情況, 最後成個服務收成3,000. <br />\n我到而家都覺得好貴, 唔知係咪俾人昆左, 不過嗰陣趕住用又唔識人無計.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1418f87e4449dd2f23e33663a6cd1f732d88c4e","tid":1754684,"uid":28668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"千千聲起跳 <br />\n大刮花再貴<br />\n都係救得幾多救幾多"},{"pid":"cedc10c67444d6ed971ab9131280f8634b0e84f6","tid":1754684,"uid":206272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要成幾千。。。"},{"pid":"be7361ebdcc5948311740ee55a9b7f42de0fee7a","tid":1754684,"uid":206272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:1